&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Note: I don&amp;#39;t need agreement. I need accuracy and completeness. If something&amp;#39;s missing or wrong, say so.
